OL,3,CNHS trust fined #200,000 after death
OL,4,Cof girl, 16, on hospital grounds
OL,6,FAn NHS Trust in Sussex has been fined
OL,7,Fmore than #200,000 for failing to
OL,8,Fprovide "safe care and treatment" to a
OL,9,Fteenage girl who died on hospital
OL,10,Fgrounds.
OL,12,FEllame Ford-Dunn, 16, was a mental
OL,13,Fhealth inpatient at Worthing Hospital
OL,14,Fin 2022.
OL,16,FShe died on the hospital site after
OL,17,Frunning from her ward.
