OL,3,CNHS trust fined #200,000 after death
OL,4,Cof girl, 16, on hospital grounds
OL,6,FOn Wednesday, University Hospitals
OL,7,FSussex NHS Foundation Trust was fined
OL,8,F#200,000 plus legal costs in a case
OL,9,Fthe judge described as "tragic."
OL,11,FThe trust offered its "heartfelt
OL,12,Fapologies" for not being able to
OL,13,Fprotect Ellame.
OL,15,FIt has since made improvements to its
OL,16,F'missing person' policy, and says it's
OL,17,Fcommitted to ensuring there are better
OL,18,Fways to care for people who are
OL,19,Fvulnerable and distressed.
