OL,3,CNHS trust fined #200,000 after death
OL,4,Cof girl, 16, on hospital grounds
OL,6,FChief Nurse, Dr Maggie Davies, said:
OL,7,F"When we appeared at last month's
OL,8,Fhearing, we acknowledged the
OL,9,Fseriousness of what happened and the
OL,10,Fdevastating impact on Ellame's family
OL,11,Fand friends.
OL,13,F"That remains true today.
OL,15,F"The loss of Ellame was a tragedy for
OL,16,Fher and for those who loved her.
OL,18,F"Colleagues involved in her care
OL,19,Fremain devastated by her death and the
OL,20,Fimpact it continues to have on her
OL,21,Ffamily and friends.
