OL,3,CNHS trust fined #200,000 after death
OL,4,Cof girl, 16, on hospital grounds
OL,6,F"We had a responsibility to protect
OL,7,Fher while she was in our care, and we
OL,8,Fare sincerely sorry that we were not
OL,9,Fable to do that.
OL,11,F"Everyone accepts that people with
OL,12,Facute mental illness should not be in
OL,13,Fgeneral hospital wards or A&E
OL,14,Fdepartments, but that does not lessen
OL,15,Four duty to keep patients safe whilst
OL,16,Fefforts are made to provide them with
OL,17,Fmore appropriate care.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
