OL,3,CNHS trust fined #200,000 after death
OL,4,Cof girl, 16, on hospital grounds
OL,6,F"Since Ellame's death, we have made
OL,7,Fsignificant improvements to our
OL,8,Fpolicies, training, and ward
OL,9,Fenvironments to prevent anything like
OL,10,Fthis happening again.
OL,12,F"Today's sentencing reflects the
OL,13,Fseriousness of what happened, and we
OL,14,Fremain committed to working with our
OL,15,FNHS partners to learn from this
OL,16,Ftragedy, and for us all to find better
OL,17,Fways of caring for patients who are
OL,18,Fvulnerable."
OL,20,FMore follows.
